Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.65,0:00:02.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here we come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.12,0:00:04.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the start of Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:06.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're going to gatherall the shards\nof the Sacred Jewel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:08.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'll destroy Naraku\nwith my Tetsusaiga!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:11.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo... who was resurrected\ninto a body made of bones and earth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.36,0:00:13.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and continues to exist through\nsouls of the dead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.13,0:00:16.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The bond she shared with Inuyasha\nremains strong...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.83,0:00:18.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I understand that, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:20.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku, Sango, Shippo and Kirara...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.84,0:00:21.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}travel back in time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.74,0:00:22.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To a Feudal Fairytale!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:24.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.88,0:02:16.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.05,0:02:20.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone... Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:23.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ayoung child?\NSo late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:45.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:50.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:07.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:11.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing, Kagome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.11,0:03:11.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:16.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit! Sit! Sit! Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:27.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... Kagome?\NWhere're you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:29.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Awalk! For a walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:36.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome's so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:38.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have to be strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:42.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:46.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I made it sweet just so\nhe could eat it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:47.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:50.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll never cook for him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:55.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe I was a bit harsh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:04:00.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This feeling!\NIt's a Sacred Jewel shard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:02.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:05.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's very faint.\NBut I feel the Sacred Jewel shard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:09.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's with her anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:10.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:13.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll be very blunt.\NYou are to blame, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:15.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:17.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All I did was speak the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:19.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's where you messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:22.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome did herbest to cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How could you say such\na cruel thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.65,0:04:27.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then... Were you able\nto eat that stuff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:31.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:33.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Avery distinct flavor.\N- Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.82,0:04:35.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You guys are strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:38.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How could you eat stuff that\nmakes yourtongue burn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:48.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's from in here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:52.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The shard seems\npure enough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:54.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:57.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone... help...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:01.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have no choice but\nto go in and see formyself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:34.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:41.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The shard of the Sacred Jewel...\nshe has one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:52.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems you have the power\nof a priestess, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:57.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh... What're you doing in\na place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is something wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could it be your soul spheres?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where are the Soul Collectors?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:09.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why're you collapsed in here\nlike this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:13.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You sure talk a lot like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.99,0:06:21.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In any case, let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:23.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:25.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're in the belly of\nthe Priestess Eater.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:28.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Priestess Eater?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:29.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the name of the demon
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:31.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who devours priestesses\nand absorbs their powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:34.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It puts up a barrier on the outside
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:37.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and allows no one but\na priestess inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:39.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So we're inside the belly\nof this demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:43.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A priestess' powers have\nno effect in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:45.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's impossible to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:46.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:49.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it looks like an\nordinary cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:52.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's useless to attempt anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:54.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:57.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not willing to die in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:06:59.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:06.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So which way should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:12.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:15.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You should justgo and say\nyou're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:16.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:18.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I REFUSE to apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:31.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This girl... just what does\nshe intend to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:34.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh boy... why'd this have to happen?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:42.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}On top of that, why'd I have to\nget stuck with Kikyo?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:47.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Umm... Doing fine, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:53.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, not me. I meant Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:56.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's always saying things\nto make people mad,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:57.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but he's doing okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:08:00.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,ljust had a fight with him earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:04.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess when he was with you,\nsuch things neverhappened, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:10.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stupid me! What am I saying?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:14.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why must I say things like that\nto Kikyo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:18.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well because...\NKikyo and Inuyasha were...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:21.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?! Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.78,0:08:22.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:31.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will destroy Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.89,0:08:34.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you don't have to fight anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:36.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:38.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:40.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:46.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh dear... I'm having such\nbad luck today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:49.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:57.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are quite amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:09:01.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Normally, a priestess wouldn't be able\nto move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:05.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meaning I'm not normal?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:06.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:07.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:09.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am a dead person anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:11.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ratherthan being burdened\nby someone like me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:15.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you have a better chance of living\nby going on alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:18.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In orderto escape from here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:21.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you must destroy the heart which\nyou'll find deeper in the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:24.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:28.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know about our chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:31.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But don't orderme around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:35.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will notgive up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:39.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you cannotgive up\nso easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:41.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can hear something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:10:00.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Kagome is very late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:03.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:06.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think you should go\nand get her, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:09.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!\NWho'd go afterthat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:11.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Acting so proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:13.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's right, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:16.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In this world, you must\nlearn to accept things with grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:19.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be honest with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:22.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's also a problem if you're\ntoohonest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:24.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:51.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those were just practice shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.78,0:11:03.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take that! And that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:28.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:41.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We {\i1}are{\i0} going to survive this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:48.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:53.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm notgoing to look for Kagome!\NI'm goin' for a walk! S'all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:10.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel the last of my souls\nstarting to fade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:12.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We must hurry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:19.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry! We must make haste!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why does this girl?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:37.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So warm... this living body through which\nblood flows.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:39.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this Kagome's strength?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:46.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha must be so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:51.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I really don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:54.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We just had an argument
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:57.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and he probably doesn't\nknow about ourpredicament.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:13:00.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we're to escape from here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:02.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we have to do it\non our own strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:06.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo, hang in there\nfor a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.84,0:13:12.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:14.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:23.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:25.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The central core of the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:28.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:31.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:33.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:49.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you destroy the heart of the demon,\nthe barrierwill disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:52.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's... the heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:13:57.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then there's no time to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:13:59.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's destroy it and\nget out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:10.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's too much even for Kagome...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:12.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.17,0:14:14.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:19.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A priestess' power and her\narrows are useless against this demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.07,0:14:21.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-That's!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:37.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's that?!\NHow gruesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,R-Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:41.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:44.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous to\nstay... here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:49.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The path!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:52.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Run! It's over if you're sealed in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:55.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! I will NOT leave you behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:05.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:07.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:15.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't there something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:17.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.31,0:15:25.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My arrows are useless against it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:28.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then... I must use something else!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:29.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:35.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I shoot these into the heart...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:44.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:16:01.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way I can retrieve\nthe shards!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:17.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way I can retrieve\nthe shards!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:34.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm borrowing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:41.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here I come, Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:52.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:57.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:16:59.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel shard\ndidn't work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:01.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The shards...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:03.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give me the remaining shards...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:06.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:11.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:15.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:34.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:40.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:42.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give me your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:49.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pray...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:51.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:54.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Believe in me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:17:59.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A-All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The shards have become one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:22.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:24.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if one shard isn't\nstrong enough...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:26.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}three shards combined are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:31.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's only one chance.\NAim well!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:55.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.52,0:20:06.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,U-Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:10.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong?\NHurry and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:22.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:27.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why didn't you give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:31.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That moment... did you believe in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:36.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're very talkative for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.06,0:20:44.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even I don't know the answer\nto yourquestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:51.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then why did you save me,\na dead person?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:56.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because if you're gone,\nsomeone would be very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:07.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you're gone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:20.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:26.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You came for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.34,0:21:31.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.45,0:21:48.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Umm... Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.27,0:23:47.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Kagome...\ndo you know Sesshomaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.58,0:23:49.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sesshomaru is Inuyasha's\nolder brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.78,0:23:51.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha's on bad terms with\NSesshomaru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.45,0:23:53.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who wields a powerful\nsword named Tokijin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.48,0:23:55.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's extremely strong and\na bit cold-hearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.65,0:23:56.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cold-hearted?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.55,0:23:58.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When Inuyasha and Koga fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.49,0:23:59.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,they'd neverget to\nthe point of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.72,0:24:01.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Sesshomaru wouldn't hesitate\nto kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.66,0:24:06.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Koga and Sesshomaru:\NA Dangerous Encounter"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.83,0:24:08.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is bad! Koga will...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.43,0:24:09.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get killed!
